window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The secrets of business writing success.</p> <p>If writing is any part of your job, you owe it to yourself to figure out how to get it done consistently, efficiently, and successfully.</p> <p>This audiobook covers the business communication skills no one teaches you in writing class:</p> <p></p> <ul> <li>How to collaborate effectively with stakeholders or subject matter experts&nbsp;</li> <li>Why the style guide is your friend and how to create one for your business&nbsp;</li> <li>The most efficient way to approach revision&nbsp;</li> <li>How to set up your projects to sail through reviews and approvals&nbsp;</li> </ul> <p><i>The Workplace Writer's Process</i> is filled with actionable advice you can use immediately to finish more projects in less time and create content. Buy it today to invest in your career success.</p>"; 
